 <a href="http://www.seagrant.sunysb.edu/">
  New York Sea Grant
 </a>
 .  Its development and operation was made possible by funds from the
 <a href="http://www.climate.noaa.gov/cpo_pa/nctp/">
  NOAA Climate Program Office Transition of Research Applications to Climate Services Program
 </a>
 . The basis of much of the
information that is research described in
 <a href="http://ams.allenpress.com/perlserv/?request=get-document&amp;doi=10.1175%2F1520-0442%282001%29014%3C0882%3AAECWSC%3E2.0.CO%3B2">
  Hirsch et al. (2000)
 </a>
 and
 <a href="http://ams.allenpress.com/perlserv/?request=get-document&amp;doi=10.1175%2F1520-0442%282002%29015%3C1101%3ASPOSEC%3E2.0.CO%3B2">
  DeGaetano et al. (2002)
